### Heading

Use the <h1> to <h6> elements to define your headings.

##### html
----------

```
<h1>h1. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h1>
<h2>h2. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h2>
<h3>h3. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h3>
<h4>h4. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h4>
<h5>h5. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h5>
<h6>h6. Modulr.css <small>Secondary text</small></h6>
```

